{"tid":1459904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港股跌114點　太古系全線受壓　國泰股價挫近半成","createTime":"2019-08-12T23:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:16:37.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8adebad9812481a6a885a90e61b2fddcf4425245","tid":1459904,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:38:32.000Z","msg":"港股走勢反覆，恒指26000點得而復失，並以全日低位收市，成交額不足600億元。<br />\n<br />\n恒指早段曾升130點，高見26069點，其後窄幅上落，尾段跌幅擴大，收市報25824點，跌114點，跌幅0.44%。<br />\n<br />\n太古系陷入政治風波，全線受壓，太古A挫逾6%，是表現最差成份股，太古地產跌超過5%，太古B及國泰挫近半成。滙控接連有高層離職，與同系恒生都跌逾1%。<br />\n<br />\n地產及收租股收壓，新世界發展跌逾3%，領展及港鐵跌2%或以上。<br />\n<br />\n手機設備股個別發展，舜宇光學升逾3%，中興通訊跌1%。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒旗下刊物公布最新收費計劃，股價急升22%。"},{"pid":"a6b947a08d7aecf73138166d682e0a8d2e58a74d","tid":1459904,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a42af2199bac7e7286d89b44626721206a47733","tid":1459904,"uid":241723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157318ead49727fb5d7a01ccd94a4adc03994f86","tid":1459904,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s burn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}